<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The first story has a probably pan character, there are at least two stories with gay characters, at least two with lesbians and a story with a trans <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The first story has a probably pan character, there are at least two stories with gay characters, at least two with lesbians and a story with a trans main character. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
